00:28:46.400 --> 00:28:47.820
Can I tell you the devil was working,

00:28:47.820 --> 00:28:49.700
he got in a small accident on the way.

00:28:50.739 --> 00:28:52.460
The devil was at work.

00:28:53.580 --> 00:28:55.159
