00:28:55.159 --> 00:28:57.700
I think it was the next day that Ms. Joyce called Holly,

00:28:57.700 --> 00:28:58.659
it might have been that evening,

00:28:58.659 --> 00:29:01.280
I don't recall exactly the details,

00:29:01.280 --> 00:29:03.659
but she said, I could hear over here,

00:29:03.659 --> 00:29:04.900
Joyce's excitement.

00:29:04.900 --> 00:29:08.500
Holly, I wanted to let you know that Muhammad got saved.

00:29:08.500 --> 00:29:11.419
Hoo, glory to God.

00:29:11.419 --> 00:29:12.859
We're excited about it.

00:29:12.859 --> 00:29:15.179
I don't know Muhammad.

