00:29:25.099 --> 00:29:26.400
It doesn't really matter.

00:29:28.619 --> 00:29:30.700
But we prayed, and guess what?

00:29:30.700 --> 00:29:35.500
We get to rejoice together in the salvation of a soul

00:29:35.500 --> 00:29:39.000
that will now spend eternity in the presence of God.

00:29:39.859 --> 00:29:43.179
I may never meet this man on this earth,

00:29:43.179 --> 00:29:48.000
but one glorious day, when we're all assembled in heaven,

00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:51.140
we'll get to see people that got saved, isn't that wonderful?

00:29:51.140 --> 00:29:52.940
And we look and we understand the importance

00:29:52.940 --> 00:29:55.659
of engaging in intercessory prayer.

00:29:55.659 --> 00:29:59.020
Let me share with you in James chapter number five.

00:29:59.020 --> 00:30:00.900
We're gonna look at a New Testament truth,

